Instacast v1.0.3
-------------------------------------------
Official Web Site: http://vemedio.com/products/instacast-mac


Installation Instructions: 
------------------
- Open "Instacast v1.0.3.dmg" and Install the App.
- Copy "keyfilemaker" app to your desktop, then open it. A terminal window will come up which will automatically generate the necessary license information. Close Terminal. 
- Enjoy.


Important Note: 
------------------
- Don't update the app. You have been warned.
- If it says that the app is damaged. Then go to the System Preferences > Security and Privacy > General > Allow apps downloaded from and Select "Anywhere".
